Create an allpass filter, connecting it to another unit

```purescript
allpass { freq: 440.0 } { sinOsc: unit }
allpass { freq: 440.0, q: 1.0 } { sinOsc: unit }
allpass 440.0 { sinOsc: unit }
```

Change an allpass filter

```purescript
allpass_ { freq: 440.0 }
allpass_ { freq: 440.0, q: 1.0 }
allpass_ 440.0
```

